      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Rolagem de Ataque Corpo a Corpo: +5, alcance 1,5 m. Acerto: 10 (2d6 + 3) dano de concussão. If o alvo is a Medium or smaller creature, the rug can give it a condição Agarrado (CD para escapar 13) instead of dealing de dano. Until the grapple ends, o alvo has the Cego and Impedido conditions, is suffocating, and takes 10 (2d6 + 3) dano de concussão at the start of each of its turns. The rug can smother only uma criatura at a time.\nWhile grappling o alvo, the rug can't take this action, the rug halves the de dano it takes (round down), and o alvo takes the same amount of de dano.</p>",
